text: David Dickinson (born 1941) is an English antiques expert and television presenter. David Dickinson may also refer to: *David T. Dickinson (1867–1930), Mayor of Cambridge, Massachusetts *David W. Dickinson (1808–1845), U.S. Representative from Tennessee *David Dickinson, author of the Lord Francis Powerscourt Mysteries series of novels *David Dickinson (academic), American scholar *David Dickinson (cricketer) (1929–1997), English cricketer ==See also== *Dave Dickenson (born 1973), Canadian football player
